title: Store perf numbers in AWS database
body_html: Previously the perf numbers are stored in https://github.com/yf225/perf-tests/tree/cpu, but we couldn't figure out a way to push the perf numbers only from master builds. This PR moves the perf number storage to AWS RDS, which allows us to have finer control over when to push the new numbers.
